restcgi::method_e

restcgi::method_e Class Reference

List of all members.

Detailed Description

Method type enumeration.

Note that these are bit flags that can be used in a mask.

See also:
http://www.w3.org/Protocols/rfc2616/rfc2616-sec9.html
